r adviser to bain  company and to coller capital in addition he is a trustee of trees for life the conservation charity dedicated to restoring the caledonian forest robin previously served as chairman of michael page international plc the ftse global specialist recruitment company from  to  he is also the former dean and president of london business school under his leadership the school was ranked number one in the world for both its mba and executive mba programmes before joining london business school in  he spent  years at bain  company he joined bain in  becoming partner in  he was elected the managing partner of bain in the uk in  and appointed the senior partner for the uk and south africa in  he was a member of the management buyout team led by mitt romney that acquired bain in  from  to  the uk business grew at over  per annum he also served as a member of the management committee compensation committee and chaired the nominating committee of the worldwide board of directors he headed both the worldwide acquisitions  alliances practice and the uk organisational enhancement and change management practice from  to  robin worked for american express international banking corporation now part of standard chartered prior to that he was employed by mann judd landau now deloitte  touche and mckinsey  company robin was a director of liberty international plc the ftse property company where he chaired the remuneration committee and contributed to the audit nominations and chairman’s committees he was also a director of shire plc the ftse pharmaceuticals company and served on its remuneration committee he is a published author on strategy acquisitions customer loyalty leadership board effectiveness and corporate governance remuneration family companies and private equity see articles robin was awarded an mba with high distinction from harvard business school where he was a baker scholar and member of the harvard business school rugby club he is a fellow of the institute of chartered accountants of england  wales and financial services authority approved person referencesedit articlesedit boards will be frozen by cautions icy hand httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesboardswillbefrozenbycautionsicyhandaspx reclaiming the boards agenda httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesreclaimingboardsagendaaspx putting your leaders where it counts httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesputtingyourleaderswhereitcountsaspx the family secrets httpwwwbaincomimagesinseadquarterlyfamilysecretspdf the leadership testing ground httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesleadershiptestinggroundaspx corporate governance the seven habits of an effective board httpwwwforbescombainhtml fixing executive pay httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesfixingexecutivepaybriefaspx a ceos guide to the new challenges of m  a leadership httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesceosguidetothenewchallengesofmaleadershipaspx achieving the promise five ways to lead mergers to results httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesachievingthepromisefivewaystoleadmergerstoresultsaspx nuking europes energy problems httpwwwbaincompublicationsarticlesnukingeuropesenergyproblemsaspx the right people in the right job httpwwwceoforumcomauarticledetailcfmcidtpaulcalthropbaininternationaltherightpeopleintherightjob external linksedit httpwwwrecruitmentinternationalcouknewsmichaelpageinternationalplcannounceappointmentofnonexecutivedirectorhtm httppeopleforbescomprofilerobinbuchanan retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerobinbuchananoldid categories living peoplebusiness educatorspeople associated with the london business schoolharvard business school alumnihidden categories year of birth missing living people navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portal